reviewText: Funny, entertaining. Can't wait to see more movies/series from these Nordic countries. Finally something totally fresh and new

Excellent series. The only reason I gave this show 4 stars and not 5 was that sometimes the English sub-titles could have been worded better. However this did not prevent me from understanding the story. Lots of interesting sub-plots and twists to the story. If they make season 2 I will definitely purchase it.
it's a pity season 2 is not available
